@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "UkooBar" where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files
or Libraries are needed. However, your Workbench must have at least
4 colours.

                             How to play?

  To play, click on any octagonal-shaped tile. If there are bars
surrounding it, either horizontally or vertically, and they are not
aligned with the tile, they will rotate by 90 degrees toward that
tile. The bars that are already aligned to the tile will not move.
If a bar is correctly aligned, a coloured rectangle will surround
it.

  When all bars are correctly aligned (all bars are surrounded by
coloured rectangles), UkooBar will show how many moves it took to
complete the game pattern, and then it will display another pattern
to play with.

  Have fun!

OPTIONS
-------

  The following buttons are shown in the game window:

@{b}Replay@{ub}: Reshuffles the current game pattern.

@{b}Colour@{ub}: Changes the colour of the rectangles surrounding
                 the bars.

@{b}'?'@{ub}:    Briefly displays the pattern to match (note that
                 you can also press on the 'Help' key).

@{b}About@{ub}:  Displays the informations about the game.


  To quit the game, click on the game window's close button or
press the 'Esc' key.

